OL,5,Crating
OL,7,FFlies, cross-contamination risks and
OL,8,Fbroken or dirty equipment were some of
OL,9,Fthe issues raised by food hygiene
OL,10,Finspectors at Wales' best restaurant,
OL,11,Fa full report has shown.
OL,13,FIn November 2025 Ynyshir Restaurant
OL,14,Fand Rooms in Machynlleth - Wales' only
OL,15,FTwo Michelin Star venue - was given a
OL,16,Ffood hygiene of one, indicating "major
OL,17,Fimprovement necessary".
