OL,3,CReport reveals dead flies at Wales'
OL,4,Cbest restaurant after one hygiene
OL,5,Crating
OL,7,FThe Machynlleth restaurant under chef
OL,8,FGareth Ward opened in 2013 and is well
OL,9,Fknown for its 30-course dinner
OL,10,Fexperience.
OL,12,FHowever, following an inspection on
OL,13,FNovember 5, 2025, the Food Standards
OL,14,FAgency awarded the establishment a
OL,15,Ffood hygiene score of just one out of
OL,16,Ffive.
