OL,4,Cbest restaurant after one hygiene
OL,5,Crating
OL,7,FThe report highlighted "major
OL,8,Fimprovement (is) necessary" in terms
OL,9,Fof "management of food safety". It
OL,10,Falso noted that "improvement (is)
OL,11,Fnecessary" regarding the "cleanliness
OL,12,Fand condition" of the facilities.
OL,14,FIn January following reports of the
OL,15,Fone rating, the venue said it took the
OL,16,Foutcome "seriously" and explained some
OL,17,Fof its "specialised" cooking methods
OL,18,F"differ from conventional kitchen
OL,19,Foperations".
