OL,5,Crating
OL,7,FHe said a re-inspection had been
OL,8,Frequested. Shortly afterwards head
OL,9,Fchef Gareth Ward insisted he was "not
OL,10,Fembarrassed" and that the "place is
OL,11,Fimmaculate".
OL,13,FNow a full environmental health report
OL,14,Fon the premises has been released via
OL,15,Fa Freedom of Information request. It
OL,16,Frefers to a number of food hygiene
OL,17,Fconcerns and 'obstruction' faced by
OL,18,Finspectors.
