OL,4,Cbest restaurant after one hygiene
OL,5,Crating
OL,7,FThe full report details how
OL,8,Fenvironmental health officers
OL,9,Frepeatedly asked to see the menu
OL,10,Fduring their inspection, which they
OL,11,Fsaid was 'vital' for officers to see
OL,12,Fas part of their inspection and was
OL,13,F"eventually" provided.
OL,15,FOfficers were then given
OL,16,Fmisinformation about the extent to
OL,17,Fwhich the restaurant's burgers were
OL,18,Fcooked.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@LO]
