OL,3,CReport reveals dead flies at Wales'
OL,4,Cbest restaurant after one hygiene
OL,5,Crating
OL,7,FThe report said: "When questioned
OL,8,Fabout burgers, we were initially
OL,9,Fadvised that they are thoroughly
OL,10,Fcooked, however, when questioned
OL,11,Ffurther, we were then told the burgers
OL,12,Fare less than thoroughly cooked.
OL,14,F"We received two copies of the food
OL,15,Fsafety policy at different stages,
OL,16,Fboth of which are dated June 3, 2025,
OL,17,Fhowever the contents are significantly
OL,18,Fdifferent. Providing mis-information
OL,19,Fto an officer conducting official
OL,20,Fcontrols, is an offence of
OL,21,Fobstruction."
