OL,7,FThe report also detailed concerns
OL,8,Fabout flies at the premises,
OL,9,Fparticularly in an area known as the
OL,10,F"smithy".
OL,12,FIt continued: "A fly paper sticky
OL,13,Fstrip was being used in the prep room
OL,14,Fnear the walk in chiller as a means of
OL,15,Fpest control had an accumulation of
OL,16,Fdead flies. Its position directly
OL,17,Fabove a food prep surface presents a
OL,18,Frisk of food below being contaminated."
