OL,5,Crating
OL,7,FThe report detailed concerns about the
OL,8,Fstorage of ready to eat raw meat and
OL,9,Fthe risk of cross-contamination. It
OL,10,Falso stated that a knife used for
OL,11,F"less than thoroughly cooked" burgers
OL,12,Fwas described as "dirty". There was
OL,13,F"no wash hand basin for food handlers"
OL,14,Fworking in the smithy.
