OL,7,FThe report also referred to
OL,8,F"significant hazards not identified"
OL,9,Fin relation to lobsters and lobster
OL,10,Fmeat, which was being served raw. The
OL,11,Freport stated: "Significant risks
OL,12,Fassociated with the service of raw
OL,13,Flobsters, specifically microbiological
OL,14,Fhazards have not been fully identified
OL,15,Fand/or controlled."
OL,17,FIt stated that no Hazard Analysis and
OL,18,FCritical Control Point (HACCP)
OL,19,Fdocument existed to cover this "high-
OL,20,Frisk" activity and that "no
OL,21,Fverification" had been carried out.
