OL,7,FFurther concerns were noted regarding
OL,8,FYnyshir's monitoring records, with
OL,9,F"inconsistencies and irregularities"
OL,10,Freported. These included the
OL,11,Fdocumentation of timings of daily
OL,12,Fcooking temperatures, delivery
OL,13,Ftemperatures, and cooling temperatures.
